<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <title>Student Restrictions and Regulations</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            margin: 20px;
        }
        
        h2 {
            color:  #00c78e;;
            text-align: center;
          
        }
        
        h3 {
            color: #333;
            margin-top: 30px;
        }
        
        p {
            line-height: 1.6;
        }
        
        .section {
            margin-bottom: 30px;
        }
        
        .section-title {
            color: #00c78e;
            font-size: 20px;
            font-weight: bold;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }
        
        .section-content {
            margin-left: 20px;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <h2>Student Restrictions and Regulations</h2>
    
    <div class="section">
        <h3 class="section-title">Attendance</h3>
        <div class="section-content">
            <p>Students are expected to attend all classes regularly. Excessive absenteeism may result in disciplinary action.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
    
    <div class="section">
        <h3 class="section-title">Code of Conduct</h3>
        <div class="section-content">
            <p>All students are required to adhere to the code of conduct set forth by the institution. Any violation may result in penalties.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
    
    <div class="section">
        <h3 class="section-title">Academic Integrity</h3>
        <div class="section-content">
            <p>Students must maintain academic integrity and avoid any form of cheating or plagiarism. Violations will be subject to disciplinary measures.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
    
    <div class="section">
        <h3 class="section-title">Library Regulations</h3>
        <div class="section-content">
            <p>Students must follow the rules and regulations of the library, including returning borrowed materials on time and maintaining a quiet study environment.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
    
    <div class="section">
        <h3 class="section-title">Campus Safety</h3>
        <div class="section-content">
            <p>Ensuring campus safety is a priority. Students are encouraged to report any suspicious activities or security concerns to campus authorities.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
    
</body>
</html>
